how java is both compiler & interpreter lan?
.class anedhi compiler create chesthadhi i.e byte code edhi machine understandable lang kadhu so ah .class ni intrepeter machine level lang lo ki
convert chesthadhi. Ikkada interpreter ante JVM

what is JDK,JRE AND JVM?
jdk anedhi jre + dev tools like javac , Javadocs consists ayyi vuntay
jre anedhi jvm+some runtime inbuilt lib consists ayyi vuntay
** but here what is jvm and how it works?
jvm anedhi few steps vuntay

1st one --> classloader --> .class file anedhanini tisukoni anni analyse chesi memory area lo ki load chesthadhi based on the data
2nd memory area--> ikkada manaki method area, heap area, stack area, pc registers, native method evi vuntay
-- method area lo only static data store chesthadhi
-- ** heap area lo instance data store chesthadhi -- main imp (objects are stored in heap area)-- instance data is objects
-- method lo rase local variables stack area lo store avvuthay (for ex: add method lo a=10, b =20, vunte a, b anevi stack area lo store chesukuntadhi)
-- pc registers ante ye instruction tarvtha ye instruction run avvali anedhi vuntadhi . ante add method, 1st do a=10, next b=20, then do a+b all these instructions what we have written in our method will store.
    java anedhi multithreaded porgrammining lan, prathi thread ki data vuntundhi dhanini thread stack antam adhi kuda stack area lo store avvudhi
-- native method ante vere lang lo rasina dhanini  ikkada execute chethe adhi native method lo ki velthunndhi (like c,c++ rasina vatini java lo execute chesthe)
3rd execution engine --> ikkada intrepeter, JIT compiler, garbage collection vuntay 
here after all above steps the intrepeter convert the bytecode to machine understandable code
-- jit compiler anedhi endhukante execution speed increase cheyyadaniki ante same multiple times execute ayithe dhanini ikkada jit compiler execute
   it is not mandatory to use
--- garbage collection anedhi manam use cheyyakunda create chesi vadhilesina objects ni clean up chesthadhi
4th and we also have native method interface and native lib for exceution of another lang code


                          JVM
                           |
                    Class loader also called classloadsubsystem(CLSS)
                           |
                           | jvm  memory area
  method area      heap area        stack area     pcregisters     native methods
                                              |
					      | execution engine
  interpreter  jit compiler garbage collection      native method interface      native method lib


