--** diff between while and do-while?
    while anedhi entry control endhukante, while loop loki velthunappude condition check chesthundhi
    them min execution for while loop is 0 because if condition fail ayithe while loop Lodhi execute avvadhu
    do-while anedhi exit control ,ikkada the min execution for dowhile is 1 ,because in do-while atleast vakasari ayina 
    statement execute avvuthundhi tarvtha condition check chesthundhi
--**sum of numbers using ternary operator?
    123--> 1+2+3
   logic --> n%9==0?9:n%9
   ye number ayina vakavela 9 tho divide ayithe dhani sum 9 avvuthundhi, vakavela divide avvakapothe dhani sum ,num%9 avvuthundhi
-- we have break and continue statemnets, break anedhi execution stop chesi loop nunchi bayatiki vachesthadhi , adhe continue ayithe 
   aa particular execution ni skip chesi continue chesthadhi
--*prime number checking, prime number ante dhaniki 1, and same number factor ayithe dhanini prime antaru ante 2 tisukunte dhaniki 1,2 matrame factors
   n=sc.nextInt();
   factorCount=0;
   for(i=2;i<n;i++)
   {
      if(n%i==0)
        factorCount++;
   }
   if(factorCount==2)
     s.o.p("primenumber");
   else
    s.o.p("not prime");
--same dhinine manam sqrt(n) varake check chesi kuda rayochu
   for(i=2;i<Math.sqrt(n);i++)
