   homogenous data tappa heterogeneous data ni store cheyyalem dhini kosam manam collections lo arraylist vundhi adhi yekkuva use chestham
--var-args: for ex nvu addition of two array numbers chedam anukunnav
   add(int[] a,int[] b) eppudu addition of 3 array numbers cheyyali ante add(int[] a,int[] b,int[] c) ila prathisari manam add cheyyali 
   adhe var args ante add(int... a)-> ila declare chesthe Yenni ayina tisukuntadhi
